<inglise>Specification of information </inglise>
<eesti>Sotsiaalmaksu maksjalt k&auml;esoleva seaduse paragrahv 10 l&otilde;ike 1 punkti 6 alusel, maksumaksjate ja maksu kinnipidajate registrist ja riikliku pensionikindlustuse registrist sama perioodi kohta saadud andmete erinevuse korral on kindlustataval &otilde;igus taotleda oma elukohaj&auml;rgselt Maksuameti kohalikult asutuselt andmete t&auml;psustamist v&otilde;i erinevuse p&otilde;hjuste selgitamist. </eesti>
<inglise>If information received from a payer of social tax pursuant to clause 10 (1) 6) of this Act, from the register of taxpayers and withholding agents and from the state pension insurance register for the same period is different, the insurable person has the right to request specification of the information or clarification of the reasons for the differences from the local Tax Board Office of his or her residence. </inglise>
<eesti>Maksuameti kohalik asutus on kohustatud hiljemalt kolme kuu jooksul taotluse saamise p&auml;evast arvates teatama kindlustatavale t&auml;psustatud andmed v&otilde;i andmete erinevuse p&otilde;hjuse ja selle k&otilde;rvaldamise t&auml;htp&auml;eva. </eesti>
<inglise>The local Tax Board Office is required to notify the insurable person of the specified information or reasons for the differences in information and of the date of elimination of such differences not later than within three months after the date of receipt of an application. </inglise>
<eesti>(15.09.99 j&otilde;ust.09.10.99 - RT I 1999, 71, 685) </eesti>
<inglise>(15.09.99 entered into force 09.10.99 - RT I 1999, 71, 685) </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 14. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 14. </inglise>
<eesti>Seaduse rakendamine </eesti>
<inglise>Implementation of Act </inglise>
<eesti>Eesti Vabariigi sotsiaalmaksu seaduse (RT 1990, 9, 102; 1991, 32, 391; 1992, 21, 302; 34, 444; RT I 1993, 65, 924; 79, 1181; 1994, 40, 656; 1995, 17, 235; 1996, 74, 1307) alusel p&auml;rast k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist tasumisele kuuluv sotsiaalmaks kantakse maksumaksja elu- v&otilde;i asukohaj&auml;rgse Maksuameti kohaliku asutuse pangakontole, nimetatud seaduse alusel tekkinud sotsiaalmaksu osade v&otilde;lad n&otilde;utakse sisse Maksuameti poolt. </eesti>
<inglise>The social tax payable pursuant to the Republic of Estonia Social Tax Act (RT 1990, 9, 102; 1991, 32, 391; 1992, 21, 302; 34, 444; RT I 1993, 65, 924; 79, 1181; 1994, 40, 656; 1995, 17, 235; 1996, 74, 1307) after the entry into force of this Act shall be transferred to the bank account of the local Tax Board Office of the residence or seat of the taxpayer; arrears of social tax arising on the basis of the specified Act shall be collected by the Tax Board. </inglise>
<eesti>Eelnimetatud summad suunatakse laekumisel isikustamata summadena riikliku pensionikindlustuse eelarvesse ja riikliku ravikindlustuse eelarvesse. </eesti>
<inglise>Upon receipt, the aforementioned amounts shall be transferred to the state pension insurance budget and state health insurance budget without reference to each insurable person separately. </inglise>
